Package: leanclust
Title: Student Performance Clustering and Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sertan", "SAFAK", , "setosfk@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lean and reproducible tools for educational data mining.
    Provides wrappers for k-means based student clustering, DTW-based
    time-series clustering via hierarchical Ward.D2 linkage,
    rule-based performance classification, IQR-based outlier detection,
    and helper utilities for summarising and visualising student
    performance. Designed as a teaching package for graduate-level
    statistical programming courses.
